{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"字符集","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/character_set","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>字符集</strong>是能讓電腦知道如何解讀<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Character\">字符</a>的編碼系統。解讀範圍包括字母、數字、標點符號、還有空白等。</p>\n<p>早期各國出於各自的語言考量，而開發各自的字符集：例如日文的漢字 JIS（有 Shift-JIS、EUC-JP 等）、繁體中文的 Big5、俄文的 KOI8-R 等等。不過支持多語言的 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Unicode\">Unicode <small>(en-US)</small></a>，逐漸成了最通用的字符集。</p>\n<p>如果字符集使用不當（像是用 Unicode 閱覽 Big5 編碼的文章），可能會看到一大堆破碎的文字。這些破碎的文字，一般被俗稱為<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BA%82%E7%A2%BC\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">亂碼</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%AD%97%E5%85%83%E7%B7%A8%E7%A2%BC\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">字元編碼</a>（維基百科）</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BA%82%E7%A2%BC\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">亂碼</a>（維基百科）</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary\">術語表</a>\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Character\">字符</a></li>\n      <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Unicode\">Unicode <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"字符集是能讓電腦知道如何解讀字符的編碼系統。解讀範圍包括字母、數字、標點符號、還有空白等。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Character set","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Conjunto de caracteres","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Jeu de caractères","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Character set (文字コード)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Character set","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Character s